T1  - The Governance of Nonprofits and Their Social Impact: Evidence from a Randomized Program in Healthcare in the Democratic Republic of Congo
AU  - Fangwa, Anicet A.
AU  - Flammer, Caroline
AU  - Huysentruyt, Marieke
AU  - Quélin, Bertrand V.
Y1  - 2023/07/14
