T1  - Punish Underperformance with Suspension: Optimal Dynamic Contracts in the Presence of Switching Cost
AU  - Cao, Ping
AU  - Sun, Peng
AU  - Tian, Feng
Y1  - 2023/06/27
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/05/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4845
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4845
